CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 22, 1945, pg. 28, reads: "Which is 'Miss Football'? - Eliane [Elaine] Richardson, Areva Lynch, Ruth Jeanne Walker and Esther Lee Rodgers are in the running for the title of 'Miss Football,' who will be selected at the Palomar Ballroom on Friday, Dec. 28. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Contenders for "Miss Football," Elaine Richardson, Areva Lynch, Ruth Jeanne Walker, and Esther Lee Rodgers posed in front of leaf patterned background in Harris Studio
